>\r\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"noprint renvois_vers_le_texte\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Less_(langage)#cite_ref-5\">&uarr;</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"indicateur-langue\">(<abbr class=\"abbr\" title=\"Langue&nbsp;: anglais\">en</abbr>)</span> <a class=\"external free\" href=\"https://gist.github.com/674726\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://gist.github.com/674726</a><small class=\"cachelinks\">&nbsp;[<a title=\"archive sur Wikiwix\" href=\"http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgist.github.com%2F674726\">archive</a>]</small>&nbsp;: comparaisons de syntaxe LESS et SASS</span></li>\r\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"noprint renvois_vers_le_texte\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Less_(langage)#cite_ref-6\">&uarr;</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external free\" href=\"http://github.com/tomyeh/ZUSS\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://github.com/tomyeh/ZUSS</a><small class=\"cachelinks\">&nbsp;[<a title=\"archive sur Wikiwix\" href=\"http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Ftomyeh%2FZUSS\">archive</a>]</small></span></li>\r\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"noprint renvois_vers_le_texte\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Less_(langage)#cite_ref-7\">&uarr;</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://github.com/marklagendijk/WinLess/issues/55#issuecomment-12863789\" rel=\"nofollow\">[1]</a><small class=\"cachelinks\">&nbsp;[<a title=\"archive sur Wikiwix\" href=\"http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fmarklagendijk%2FWinLess%2Fissues%2F55%23issuecomment-12863789\">archive</a>]</small> WinLess github Issue \"License Information\"</span></li>\r\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"noprint renvois_vers_le_texte\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Less_(langage)#cite_ref-8\">&uarr;</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/matthewdl/Crunch/blob/master/LICENSE.txt\" rel=\"nofollow\">Crunch\'s LICENSE.txt at github</a><small class=\"cachelinks\">&nbsp;[<a title=\"archive sur Wikiwix\" href=\"http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fmatthewdl%2FCrunch%2Fblob%2Fmaster%2FLICENSE.txt\">archive</a>]</small> Crunch\'s LICENSE.txt at github</span></li>\r\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"noprint renvois_vers_le_texte\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Less_(langage)#cite_ref-9\">&uarr;</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://chirpy.codeplex.com/license\" rel=\"nofollow\">[2]</a><small class=\"cachelinks\">&nbsp;[<a title=\"archive sur Wikiwix\" href=\"http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fchirpy.codeplex.com%2Flicense\">archive</a>]</small> Chirpy License Information at CodePlex</span></li>\r\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"noprint renvois_vers_le_texte\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Less_(langage)#cite_ref-10\">&uarr;</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.normalesup.org/~simonet/soft/ow/eclipse-less.fr.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eclipse Plugin for LESS homepage</a><small class=\"cachelinks\">&nbsp;[<a title=\"archive sur Wikiwix\" href=\"http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.normalesup.org%2F~simonet%2Fsoft%2Fow%2Feclipse-less.fr.html\">archive</a>]</small> Eclipse Plugin for LESS homepage</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><span id=\"Liens_externes\" class=\"mw-headline\">Liens externes</span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"indicateur-langue\">(<abbr class=\"abbr\" title=\"Langue&nbsp;: anglais\">en</abbr>)</span> <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://lesscss.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">site officiel Less</a><small class=\"cachelinks\">&nbsp;[<a title=\"archive sur Wikiwix\" href=\"http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=http%3A%2F%2Flesscss.org%2F\">archive</a>]</small></li>\r\n<li><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/cloudhead/less.js\" rel=\"nofollow\">Less source code repository (Git)</a><small class=\"cachelinks\">&nbsp;[<a title=\"archive sur Wikiwix\" href=\"http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fcloudhead%2Fless.js\">archive</a>]</small></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><span id=\"Articles_connexes\" class=\"mw-headline\">Articles connexes</span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a title=\"Sass (langage)\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sass_(langage)\">Sass</a></li>\r\n<li><a title=\"Pr&eacute;processeur CSS\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pr%C3%A9processeur_CSS\">Pr&eacute;processeur CSS</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><strong>Less</strong> est un langage dynamique de g&eacute;n&eacute;ration de <a title=\"Feuilles de style en cascade\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Feuilles_de_style_en_cascade\">CSS</a> con&ccedil;u par Alexis Sellier. Initialement inspir&eacute; par <a title=\"Sass (langage)\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sass_(langage)\">Sass</a>, il l\'influence &agrave; son tour avec l\'apparition de la syntaxe \"SCSS\" par laquelle Sass reprend des &eacute;l&eacute;ments de la syntaxe CSS classique. Le principe de Less est en effet de ne pas rompre avec la syntaxe CSS<sup id=\"cite_ref-compare_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Less_(langage)#cite_note-compare-2\">2</a></sup>&nbsp;: tout code CSS est aussi du code Less valide et s&eacute;mantiquement &eacute;quivalent.</p>\r\n<p>Less y ajoute notamment les m&eacute;canismes suivants&nbsp;: variables, imbrication, <a title=\"Mixin\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mixin\">mixins</a>, <a title=\"Op&eacute;rateur (informatique)\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Op%C3%A9rateur_(informatique)\">op&eacute;rateurs</a> et <a class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fonction informatique\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fonction_informatique\">fonctions</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'public%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fuploads%2Fless.jpg', '2018-04-14 21:10:17', '2018-04-14 21:10:17');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `content_right`, `image`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(4, 'jQuery', '<p>La <a title=\"Biblioth&egrave;que logicielle\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Biblioth%C3%A8que_logicielle\">biblioth&egrave;que</a> contient notamment les fonctionnalit&eacute;s suivantes&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>parcours et modification du <a title=\"Document Object DBConnexion\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Document_Object_Model\">DOM</a> (y compris le support des s&eacute;lecteurs <a title=\"Feuilles de style en cascade\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Feuilles_de_style_en_cascade\">CSS</a> 1 &agrave; 3 et un support basique de <a title=\"XPath\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/XPath\">XPath</a>)&nbsp;;</li>\r\n<li>&eacute;v&eacute;nements&nbsp;;</li>\r\n<li>effets visuels et animations&nbsp;;</li>\r\n<li>manipulations des <a title=\"Feuilles de style en cascade\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Feuilles_de_style_en_cascade\">feuilles de style en cascade</a> (ajout/suppression des classes, d\'attributs&hellip;)&nbsp;;</li>\r\n<li><a title=\"Ajax (informatique)\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ajax_(informatique)\">Ajax</a>&nbsp;;</li>\r\n<li><a title=\"Plugin\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plugin\">plugins</a>&nbsp;;</li>\r\n<li>Utilitaires (version du <a title=\"Navigateur web\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Navigateur_web\">navigateur web</a>&hellip;).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Depuis sa cr&eacute;ation en 2006 et notamment &agrave; cause de la complexification croissante des interfaces Web, jQuery a connu un large succ&egrave;s aupr&egrave;s des d&eacute;veloppeurs Web et son apprentissage est aujourd\'hui un des fondamentaux de la formation aux technologies du Web. Il est &agrave; l\'heure actuelle la <em>librairie front-end</em> la plus utilis&eacute;e au monde (plus de la moiti&eacute; des sites Internet en ligne int&egrave;grent jQuery).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><span id=\"Usage\" class=\"mw-headline\">Usage</span></h2>\r\n<p>jQuery se pr&eacute;sente comme un unique fichier JavaScript de <span class=\"nowrap\">247 <abbr class=\"abbr\" title=\"kibioctet\"><a class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kibioctet\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kibioctet#Multiples_normalis&eacute;s\">Kio</a></abbr></span> (<span class=\"nowrap\">92,2 <abbr class=\"abbr\" title=\"kio\"><a class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kibioctet\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kibioctet#Multiples_normalis&eacute;s\">kio</a></abbr></span> dans sa version minimalis&eacute;e par la suppression des commentaires et caract&egrave;res d\'espacements, et 32 kio en ayant fait l&rsquo;objet d&rsquo;une compression <a title=\"Gzip\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gzip\">gzip</a>) contenant toutes les fonctions de base<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/JQuery#cite_note-3\">3</a></sup>. Il peut &ecirc;tre inclus dans toute page web en utilisant le code suivant&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<div class=\"mw-highlight mw-content-ltr\" dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<pre><span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nt\">script</span> <span class=\"na\">src</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">\"/chemin/vers/jQuery.js\"</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"nt\">script</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>La biblioth&egrave;que jQuery peut &ecirc;tre appel&eacute;e de deux mani&egrave;res diff&eacute;rentes&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>via la fonction <code lang=\"jQuery\">jQuery</code>, ou <code lang=\"jQuery\">$</code>. Cette fonction est cha&icirc;nable (elle retourne l\'objet appelant). Par exemple&nbsp;:\r\n<div class=\"mw-highlight mw-content-ltr\" dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<pre><span class=\"nx\">$</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"div.test\"</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"nx\">add</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"p.quote\"</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"nx\">addClass</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"blue\"</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"nx\">slideDown</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"slow\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>via l\'objet <code lang=\"jquery\">$</code>. Par exemple&nbsp;:\r\n<div class=\"mw-highlight mw-content-ltr\" dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<pre><span class=\"nx\">$</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">each</span><span class=\"p\">([</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">],</span> <span class=\"kd\">function</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\r\n	<span class=\"nb\">document</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">write</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">this</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\r\n<span class=\"p\">});</span>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Voici un exemple d\'Ajax avec jQuery&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<div class=\"mw-highlight mw-content-ltr\" dir=\"ltr\">\r\n<pre><span class=\"nx\">$</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">document</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"nx\">ready</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kd\">function</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>                    <span class=\"c1\">// Lorsque le document est charg&eacute;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"nx\">$</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\".load_page_on_click\"</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"nx\">click</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kd\">function</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>   <span class=\"c1\">// Lorsque l&rsquo;on clique sur un &eacute;l&eacute;ment d\'attribut class \"load_page_on_click\"</span>\r\n        <span class=\"kd\">var</span> <span class=\"nx\">email</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nx\">$</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"input[name=email]\"</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"nx\">val</span><span class=\"p\">();</span> <span class=\"c1\">// Variable contenant la valeur d\'un &eacute;l&eacute;ment input d\'attribut name \"email\"</span>\r\n        <span class=\"nx\">$</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nx\">ajax</span><span class=\"p\">({</span>                         <span class=\"c1\">// Ex&eacute;cution d&rsquo;une requ&ecirc;te Ajax avec la configuration donn&eacute;e par l\'objet suivant :</span>\r\n            <span class=\"nx\">async</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"true\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>               <span class=\"c1\">// - requ&ecirc;te asynchrone</span>\r\n            <span class=\"nx\">type</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"GET\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>                 <span class=\"c1\">// - type HTTP GET</span>\r\n            <span class=\"nx\">url</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"mapage.php\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>           <span class=\"c1\">// - URL de la page &agrave; charger</span>\r\n            <span class=\"nx\">data</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"email=\"</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"nb\">encodeURIComponent</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nx\">email</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"&amp;action=get_email\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"c1\">// - donn&eacute;es &agrave; envoyer</span>\r\n            <span class=\"nx\">error</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kd\">function</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nx\">errorData</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span> <span class=\"c1\">// - fonction de rappel en cas d&rsquo;erreur</span>\r\n                <span class=\"nx\">$</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"#error\"</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"nx\">html</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nx\">errorData</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\r\n            <span class=\"p\">},</span>\r\n            <span class=\"nx\">success</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kd\">function</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nx\">data</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>    <span class=\"c1\">// - fonction de rappel pour le traitement des donn&eacute;es re&ccedil;ues en cas de succ&egrave;s</span>\r\n                <span class=\"nx\">$</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"#container\"</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"nx\">html</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nx\">data</span><span class=\"p\">);</span> <span class=\"nx\">$</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"#error\"</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"nx\">append</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Contenu charg&eacute;\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\r\n            <span class=\"p\">}</span>\r\n        <span class=\"p\">});</span> <span class=\"c1\">// Fermeture de l\'appel &agrave; la fonction $.ajax</span>\r\n    <span class=\"p\">});</span>     <span class=\"c1\">// Fermeture de la fonction de rappel du $(\".load_page_on_click\").click</span>\r\n<span class=\"p\">});</span>         <span class=\"c1\">// Fermeture de la fonction de rappel du $(document).ready</span>\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>On peut aussi remplacer la premi&egrave;re ligne du script <code class=\"mw-highlight\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"nx\">$</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">document</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"nx\">ready</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kd\">function</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span></code> par <code class=\"mw-highlight\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"nx\">$</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kd\">function</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span></code>.</p>\r\n<h2><span id=\"Modules_d.27extension\"></span><span id=\"Modules_d\'extension\" class=\"mw-headline\">Modules d\'extension</span></h2>\r\n<p>Parce que jQuery est un constructeur de code source libre, d\'autres personnes utilisent sa syntaxe pour cr&eacute;er de nouveaux <a title=\"Plugin\" href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plugin\">modules d\'extension</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/JQuery#cite_note-4\">4</a></sup> afin d\'ajouter d\'autres fonctionnalit&eacute;s aux biblioth&egrave;ques.</p>\r\n<h2><span id=\"Notes_et_r.C3.A9f.C3.A9rences\"></span><span id=\"Notes_et_r&eacute;f&eacute;rences\" class=\"mw-headline\">Notes et r&eacute;f&eacute;rences</span></h2>\r\n<div class=\"references-small decimal\">\r\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\">\r\n<ol class=\"references\">\r\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"noprint renvois_vers_le_texte\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/JQuery#cite_ref-1\">&uarr;</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"ouvrage\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://blog.jquery.com/2017/03/20/jquery-3-2-1-now-available/\" rel=\"nofollow\">&laquo;&nbsp;<cite style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span class=\"lang-en\" lang=\"en\">jQuery 3.2.1 Is Now Available, With Some Hotfixes</span></cite>&nbsp;&raquo;</a><small class=\"cachelinks\">&nbsp;[<a title=\"archive sur Wikiwix\" href=\"http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.jquery.com%2F2017%2F03%2F20%2Fjquery-3-2-1-now-available%2F\">archive</a>]</small> <small style=\"line-height: 1em;\">(consult&eacute; le <span class=\"nowrap\">20 mars 2017</span>)</small></span></span></li>\r\n<li id=\"cite_note-JQuery-2\"><span class=\"noprint renvois_vers_le_texte\"><a href=\"https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/JQuery#cite_ref-JQuery_2-0\">&uarr;</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"ouvrage\"><span class=\"indicateur-langue\">(<abbr class=\"abbr\" title=\"Langue&nbsp;: anglais\">en</abbr>)</